{
  "resourceType": "Questionnaire",
  "name": "HeartScore",
  "title": "HEART Score for Major Cardiac Events",
  "status": "active",
  "subjectType": "Patient",
  "description": "Bedside risk-stratification tool for adult emergency department patients with chest pain suggestive of acute coronary syndrome. Predicts the 6-week risk of major adverse cardiac events (MACE: all-cause mortality, AMI, coronary revascularization). Source: Six AJ, Backus BE, Kelder JC. Neth Heart J. 2008;16(6):191-196; Backus BE et al. Crit Pathw Cardiol. 2010;9(3):164-169; Backus BE et al. Int J Cardiol. 2013;168(3):2153-2158.",
